title: Veteran Cut Candidates
itunes:title: Veteran Cut Candidates
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the news around the NFL including Tyreek Hill suspension status (6:32), Zeke's holdout (17:56) and Drew Lock's chances as a NFL QB. (24:30). Gregg goes over his sub-banger "Veteran Cut Candidates (33:25) and the heroes give their one big thought to close the show.
